description: September of 2021… after studying absolutely zero Chinese for a full year, I had to take a language-ability test at the university, via Zoom conference call.  I'm staring at the screen because that's the portal to the professor who is administering the test (in case you can't tell, I'm not reading anything, these answers are very much "off the dome").
